<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>7things on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/slug/7things/</link><description>Recent content in 7things on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2019 02:26:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/slug/7things/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>爱子七不责</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/7things/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2019 02:26:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/7things/</guid><description>文章讲述了爱子七不责的原则，即在特定情况下不要责备孩子。这包括在公众场合给予孩子尊严，在孩子已经感到愧悔后不再责备他们，在晚上睡觉前和正吃饭时避免责备，以及在孩子高兴、哭泣或生病时都应给予关爱而非指责。这些原则旨在保护孩子的身心健康。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/7things/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>